# SHError.Code.customCatalogInvalidURL

**Case**

The error code to indicate that the format for the custom catalog URL is invalid.

## Declaration

```swift
case customCatalogInvalidURL
```

## Catalog errors

- **SHError.Code.customCatalogInvalid**: The error code to indicate when the custom catalog fails to load due to an invalid format.
